<h1 id="maintain-impairment-indicators-on-individual-assets">Maintain impairment indicators on individual assets</h1>


<p>Use this task to learn how to maintain impairment indicators on individual assets.</p>
<p>Run the task 'Setup impairment accounting common parameters' prior to this running this procedure.</p>
<p>This task uses the JPMF demo company data.</p>
<h2 id="update-impairment-indicator-on-a-single-fixed-asset">Update impairment indicator on a single fixed asset</h2>
<ol>
<li>Go to Fixed assets &gt; Fixed assets &gt; Fixed assets.</li>
<li>In the list, find and select the desired record.
<ul>
<li>Example: TOOLM-000006</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Click Books.</li>
<li>Click Functions.</li>
<li>Click Update impairment indicators.</li>
<li>Click New.</li>
<li>In the Modify date field, enter a date.
<ul>
<li>Example: 2013-04-01</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Description field, type a value.</li>
<li>In the Undiscounted cash flow field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>In this example, enter field '3900000.'</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Recoverable amount field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>In this example, enter field '3350226.'</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Click Save.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="update-impairment-indicator-on-the-impairment-management-form">Update impairment indicator on the impairment management form</h2>
<ol>
<li>Go to Fixed assets &gt; .. &gt; .. &gt; Impairment management.</li>
<li>Click Query.</li>
<li>In the Criteria field for the fixed asset group row, click the drop-down button to open the lookup.</li>
<li>Click OK.</li>
<li>In the list, find and select the desired record.
<ul>
<li>TOOLM-000007</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the list, find and select the desired record.
<ul>
<li>TOOLM-000008</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Click Update impairment indicators.</li>
<li>In the list, mark the selected row.
<ul>
<li>Select the record with Fixed asset number 'TOOLM-000007.'</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Modify date field, enter a date.
<ul>
<li>Define date = 2013-04-01</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Description field, type a value.</li>
<li>In the Undiscounted cash flow field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>Enter 2500000.00.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Recoverable amount field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>Enter = 2000000.00.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the list, find and select the desired record.
<ul>
<li>Select the row with Fixed asset number 'TOOLM-000008.'</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Modify date field, enter a date.</li>
<li>In the Description field, type a value.</li>
<li>In the Undiscounted cash flow field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>Enter 2000000.00.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>In the Recoverable amount field, enter a number.
<ul>
<li>Enter 1500000.00.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Click Update indicator.</li>
</ol>
</article>
